room_title: Escape room "Demolition Abduction" by Amazing Escapes of Boise in Boise
room_address: 6555 W. Overland Rd., Suite 120, Boise, ID 83709
room_description:
You've been abducted by a ruthless gang who have mistaken you for undercover cops. They've taken you to an old abandoned building that is scheduled for demolition.
Having been locked up and left for dead, can you escape the building before it comes crashing down?!
